'''Karl Aulenbach''' was a [[Germany|German]] [[Canoe racing|sprint canoeist]] who competed in the late 1930s. He won a silver medal in the K-4 1000 m event at the [[1938 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships]] in [[Vaxholm]].

